Peragro Tempus Wiki:Copyrights

From Peragro Tempus Wiki

All material in or added to the Peragro Tempus Wiki is covered by CC-by-sa [1]. Please be sure that if you are adding material to this Wiki it is original material or is compatible with that license. This means the material should be in a compatible open license, public domain, fair use or otherwise with minimal restrictions on use. If you use material from other sources, regardless of the source, those sources should be identified to remain in compliance with our own licensing.

If you wish to use information or material from the PT wiki elsewhere, we are happy to see you do so. Please note that the CC-by-sa license does require that you name your source(s) and provide the same free access to our work for those who wish to use it.
